generateConstantOrbitData():
  write constant orbital values as text to an image

overlayOrbitData():
  overlay the image for the constant values
  write other changing params to data overlay

void initControls():
  initialize sliders and buttons

void overlayFPS():
  calculate an average of the fps from the frame times for as many as the past 50 frames; discard half of this data when 50 frames are aquired, keeping the latest 25 frames
  write this fps data to the screen

void draw():
  overlay fps and orbit data
  correct 2d slider values to invert y values (such that bottom of screen is x axis)
